{{More footnotes|date=January 2018}} {{Infobox television | show_name = Acting Dead | genre = Horror, Comedy | creator = Brian Beacock | writer = Brian Beacock | director = Alan David Morgan | starring = Brian Beacock, Jillian Clare, Chris Galya, Patrika Darbo, Paul Nygro, John Yelvington | composer = Jamie Forsyth | num_seasons = 1 | num_episodes = 8 | producer = Susan Bernhardt, Brian Beacock, Paul Nygro | cinematography = Jared Hoy | company = Leonian | website = http://actingdead.com/index.html }}
'''''Acting Dead''''' is an American satirical dark comedy about the world of [[Hollywood]] [[zombies]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://actingdead.com/index.html|title=Home of the Delicious Zomedy Series - ACTING DEAD|website=Actingdead.com|access-date=2017-04-17}}</ref> The series focuses on Tate Blodgett ([[Brian Beacock]]), a zombie, and Alex Carbonneux ([[Jillian Clare]]), a ghost, as they both struggle with their new [[afterlife]].
== Episodes == * Episode 1: Career Suicide * Episode 2: Throw The Switch! * Episode 3: Polterguise * Episode 4: Talent and Brains * Episode 5: The "X" Is Silent But Deadly * Episode 6: This Town Needs an Exorcist * Episode 7: Take You Out for a Bite * Episode 8: Money Back Scarentee
