{{unsourced|date=May 2018}}
A '''community bulletin board''' (CBB) is a [[digital signage]] system that [[Public, educational, and government access|public, educational, and government access]] [[cable television]] providers use as a [[Barker channel]] to keep communities up to date of events listings, weather and other news that can be delivered by using [[digital on-screen graphic]]s.  The electronic [[bulletin board]] concept is a form of [[Technological convergence]].

